                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The Marauders draw and fire a barrage of arrows from their shortbows. The salvo is a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 60 feet that deals @Damage[4d8[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:27|basic|options:area-effect] save). When the Marauders are reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
